    "ABOUT1": "Who are we?",
    "ABOUT2": "Kanglogo.com is a professional service provider in creating logos, banners, icons, illustrations, and other graphic designs. Established in 2021, we have served thousands of clients from domestic and international markets who have entrusted us with their logo and branding design needs. We serve various types of businesses, ranging from micro, small, and medium enterprises to personal websites. Our focus is to provide the best quality service to meet your graphic design needs. We have a creative and experienced team to produce logo and branding designs that suit your business identity. By choosing Kanglogo.com, you will get the best graphic design services to enhance your business image.",
    "ABOUT3": "What makes Kanglogo.com different from other graphic design service providers? Here are some reasons why you should choose Kanglogo.com:",
    "ABOUT4": "We offer affordable and transparent prices for every service we offer. You can see our price list on our website and choose a package that suits your budget and needs.",
    "ABOUT5": "We offer an easy and fast process to get the logo and branding design you want. You only need to fill out the brief, make a payment, wait for the design work, give feedback, and receive the final file.",
