    "TERM22": "We guarantee that the designs we create are original and we can prove it through sketches or our work on paper. After the design is approved or purchased by the client, copyright and patent rights to the design will be fully owned by the client. However, it should be noted that the design that is the client’s copyright is the final design that has been approved, whether it has been revised or not. Initial designs or designs not selected by clients will remain ours and we have the right to sell or reuse them as our assets. After delivering the design and license documents to clients, clients will become official owners of copyright and patent rights to approved or purchased designs.",
